text: Motion
Motion
Motion

Mei, about the event,
truly well done.

Haha, thanks, thanks~
But isn't the one who's really tired Fuyuko-chan?

Today's MVP? Wasn't it?
Someone who really worked hard like that!

Well, everyone did their best,
so everyone's the MVP.

Hmm~
Well, let's go with that!

But you know, I can't forget
about Fuyuko-chan today.

The coolness of an idol, you know~
I was thinking about what that really means.

I see, it seems like it was
a pretty good inspiration for you.

But just admiring is fine,
coolness is Mei's domain, right?
Haha, that's true too~

I'm going to become even cooler
from now on.

Even more so,
I want to be absolutely amazing!
With "Straylight"!
We can definitely achieve that,
the three of us.

Huh? Producer-san,
isn't that wrong?

We're forgetting someone
who can become absolutely amazing with us!
Haha!
